{"tid":2043348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美中關係惡化   傳美國出售香港領事館宿舍","createTime":"2020-05-30T10:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T10:57:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4511821cb4cb6059341a22483d0127cb0dc8eb","tid":2043348,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:53:37.000Z","msg":"在美國和中國關係愈趨惡化及美方有意取消給予香港特殊待遇之下，有香港媒體報導，美方正出售駐港總領事館的一批宿舍房產，目前市值超過港幣100億元（約新台幣386億元）。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府持有的這些宿舍房產已有72年，位於港島豪宅區壽山村道，合共有6棟超級洋房，近日開始秘密招標出售。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，根據土地註冊處的資料，這些地方的業主為「THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA」，美國於1948年以31.5萬元購入地皮（土地），當時地皮建有6棟洋房，用作美國駐港總領事館員工宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3182366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182366&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2B9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=a52af63e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3182366&h=96e198bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3182366</a>"},{"pid":"268d6638f45abf2802d6c6023955860b12af1b4b","tid":2043348,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"撤僑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275e84cbacfd50dc54ec2805019f7867fc3f6022","tid":2043348,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"1948年支共都未掌權<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}